Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(350,345)\fs19}2024年2月23日  第35層  迷宮森林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼夢話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,396)}你有那隻蜥蜴能負責回復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,396)}沒必要分配給你回復水晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎不上前線  根本就用不到水晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是西莉卡這樣的小孩子偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人們可不會幫我回復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具什麼的我也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會再和你們組隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我加入的隊伍可是有一大把的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回復道具已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜  畢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜  畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我一個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根羽毛是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是馴獸師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能救你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己能夠單獨突破森林迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根羽毛  有沒有設定道具名稱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}畢娜的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要還留有畢娜的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就還有復活的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在47層的南部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個名為「回憶之丘」的野外迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座丘頂所盛開的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就是用來復活使魔的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,47層…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能夠支付一些成本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一次也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聽說使魔的主人不去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朵花就不會盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我這項情報就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我努力提高等級的話  總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活只有在死去後的三天內才有效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…畢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  有三天足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}烏木匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}烏木匕首\N銀線甲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}烏木匕首\N銀線甲\N月光夾克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}烏木匕首\N銀線甲\N月光夾克\N妖精之靴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}烏木匕首\N銀線甲\N月光夾克\N妖精之靴\N弗羅裡特腰帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些道具也能抵上個五、六級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去的話  應該沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…要為我做到這個程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你答應我不笑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和我妹妹很像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雖然我想這點應該完全不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和我來這裡的理由並不衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫西莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段期間請多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(350,345)\fs19}第35層  密歇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  發現西莉卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就和我們組隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會帶你去有趣的地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很感謝你們來邀請我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最近我會和這個人一起組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的粉絲吧  相當受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是把我當成吉祥物才來邀請我罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我被他們稱為龍使西莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此變得自負…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定趕得上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥的家在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是在50層
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過來回挺麻煩的  我就住在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  這裡的芝士蛋糕很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這不是西莉卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然從森林裡逃出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那隻蜥蜴去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我絕對會讓牠活過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  就是說你們要去回憶之丘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以你的等級能夠攻略那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個迷宮的難度並不高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被這孩子騙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來也不怎麼強嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說得那麼刁鑽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAO是你玩的第一個MMO遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在哪個網絡遊戲中都有很多改變人格的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這些人之中也有人主動去扮演壞人的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們頭上的光標是綠色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一旦犯罪了  光標就會變成橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之中還有Player Killer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指殺害玩家的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為紅名玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然去殺人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以往的遊戲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演壞人也是件有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在SAO中性質就不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人哥是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你救了我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成你安慰我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  西莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  芝士蛋糕上的真是太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請問甜品怎麼還沒有上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說我還想再多聊一會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被他笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西莉卡  還沒睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記和你說明47層的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要明天再說？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  我也正想去問你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西莉卡  怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥  那個道具是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp40}　{\fsp1}Mirage Sphere{\r}\N這個叫幻影球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是47層的主街區
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是回憶之丘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以順著這條路走…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有敲門的話  是聽不見屋內的聲音的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將竊聽技能練到很高的話就可以聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然幾乎沒什麼人會把這技能練得很高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要偷聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(350,345)\fs19}2024年2月24日  第47層  芙洛莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像夢境之國一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一層被大家稱為花之庭園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個樓層都佈滿了花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一發生了意外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說讓你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要用這個轉移水晶逃走  到哪個城鎮都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著這條路走下去  就會到回憶之丘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  桐人哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  西莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙其實很弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人哥  救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}救我  不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有點難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥  可以問問你妹妹的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然問這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說我和她很像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然打聽現實世界的事是很不禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以說給我聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從她出生時起我們就一起長大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她可能不知道這事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許正因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會和她保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父是個嚴厲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我八歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就強行讓我們去附近的道場練習劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我練了兩年就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還因此被祖父打了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後妹妹她說著「我會算上哥哥的份加倍練習的  請不要打他了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後她努力練習  還打進了全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我一直對她感到內疚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該還有其它想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你  大概也是因為會覺得是在向妹妹賠罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得桐人哥的妹妹並沒有恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於不喜歡的事物是努力不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是真的很喜歡劍道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是被你安慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  是這樣的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活的花就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  應該就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}聖靈之花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣畢娜就會活過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這裡附近有很多強大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到城鎮後再讓牠復活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜也一定希望你那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡埋伏的人  快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅…羅莎莉亞小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能識破我的隱匿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵技能相當高呢  劍士小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你那樣子  應該是成功得到聖靈之花了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就趕緊把花交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行哦  羅莎莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  橙色公會「泰坦之手」的會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼稱呼你會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  羅莎莉亞小姐的光標是綠色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單的手段罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠色玩家負責尋找獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把他們帶到橙色玩家埋伏好的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天偷聽我們談話的  應該也是你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這兩週你加入的那個隊伍…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我在確認那個隊伍的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他們在冒險中大賺一筆的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個我最期待的獵物跑掉了雖然很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你去尋找稀有道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你明明知道這些事還陪著這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你真的被她引誘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  哪個都不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正在找你  羅莎莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在十天前襲擊了一個名為「銀色旗幟」的公會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長以外的四人全部遇害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那群沒錢的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是會長的那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天從早到晚都在最前線的傳送門廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭著尋找能夠替他報仇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並沒有要求殺了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說能讓你們進監獄就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠明白那傢伙的心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼認真像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:18:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在這裡殺了人  也沒有任何證據確認對方在現實中死去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  你們不如更擔心一下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥  人數太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我讓你逃走之前  你就準備好水晶在旁邊看著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有盾的單手劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是「黑色劍士」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅莎莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  是在最前線SOLO的封弊者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是攻略組的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻略組？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻略組的人怎麼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們趕緊給我殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的道具全搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥…得去救他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼  趕緊殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每10秒400左右的傷害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你們7人能夠給予我的傷害總量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的等級是78  HP是14500
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥回復技能所提供的自動回復量為每10秒600點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你們攻擊幾個小時都不可能打倒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅只是數字上的增加就會帶來懸殊的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是等級制MMO不合理的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的委託人用全部財產所買來的迴廊水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口設定在監獄區域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所有人就傳送到監獄裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你傷害我這個綠色玩家的話  你也會變成橙色…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前面  我可是SOLO玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成橙色一兩天根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  西莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果把你當成了誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕先和你說的話  你會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人哥是好人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  離開前線已經五天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趕快回去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟…竟然是攻略組  真是厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管多少年都到不了那個程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等級只是一個數字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界裡再強大  也只不過是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些  還有更重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次在現實世界裡見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就又能成為朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…絕對會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  把畢娜叫回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,170)\be1\frz10\fs15}畢娜的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,165)\be1\frz10\fs15}聖靈之花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好多  好多話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今天的精彩冒險的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:21:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅一天的哥哥的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  圈內事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
